name: DispatchTimeoutResult
desc: A result value indicating whether a dispatch operation finished before a specified time.

items.name: case success
items.desc: Indicates that a dispatch operation successfully finished before the specified time elapsed.

items.name: case timedOut
items.desc: Indicates that a dispatch operation failed to finish before the specified time elapsed.

items.name: static func != (DispatchTimeoutResult, DispatchTimeoutResult) -> Bool
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether two values are not equal.
